  "title": "quantity surveyor",
  "description": "<p>Job Description &amp; Requirements</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Taking off quantities</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Pre and post contract administration</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Prepare VO, claims</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Source for sub-contractors, suppliers and etc</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Provide support in any other adhoc duties as assigned by superior from time to time.</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Possess Diploma in Building or Quantity Surveying or its equivalent</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>One to two years working experience is required in pre-tender &amp; post-tender of schools, condominium &amp; other building projects.</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Analytical and meticulous with strong interpersonal and good negotiation skill.</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Able to multi-task, initiative and driven to learn</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Must be organized, independent with minimum supervision, good sense of responsibilities and resourceful</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Knowledge in ISO will be an added advantage</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Able to start work in short notice</strong></li>\n</ul>",
